reviewText: If you already know how to use Inventor you will learn one thing or two with this course but you will not gain any considerable skills.  If you don't know how to use Inventor this will definitely not help you to learn it.  This course shows some advanced tools, but it just shows a little of everything but nothing in depth. The questions don’t really test your knowledge of Inventor, they just test your memory.
not really good. the options of some quiz questions are completely wrong and there are typos which made me really confusing.

It is so helpful to get the basic skills and key features. But the test at the beginning of the course was ment to check the knowledge before the course, however it requires to pass with at least 80%. I thought it should require any rate at the beginning. But it is just my opinion
